Transmit Radio with Raspberri PI

apt-get install libsndfile1-dev
git clone https://github.com/ChristopheJacquet/PiFmRds.git
cd PiFmRds/src
make clean
make

GPIO4 Pin 7 on Raspberry Pi is the Antenna/transmit pin.
  Connect a cable to it to increase transmit strenth

sudo ./pi_fm_rds -freq 102.000 -audio sound.wav -ps KMOD -rt 'Rockin!'

convert mp3 to wav:
  apt-get install mpg123
  mpg123 -w ouput.wav input.mp3

